- **Coverage Delta**: Exercises the two `Objects.requireNonNull` guard lines at ~2241–2242. Documents the
  exact exception type and message contract, preventing future refactors from accidentally changing `requireNonNull`
  to a weaker check and breaking caller assumptions.

